'''Kamikoso Shrine''' (かみこそじんじゃ) is a {{ill|lt=Shinto shrine|Q845945|qid=Q845945|1=Shinto shrine}} enshrined in {{ill|lt=Nagahama|Q844130|qid=Q844130|1=Nagahama, Shiga}}, {{ill|lt=Shiga Prefecture|Q131358|qid=Q131358|1=Shiga Prefecture}}.

=== Enshrined deities ===
* Principal deity
** {{ill|lt=Kusanohime|Q11365189|qid=Q11365189|lt=Kusanohime-no-Mikoto|1=Hayato Nakamura}}
* Associated deities
** {{ill|lt=Ōnamuchi|Q702140|qid=Q702140|lt=Ōnamuchi-no-Mikoto|1=Ōnamuchi-no-Mikoto}}
** {{ill|qid=Q8009611|lt=Kotoshironushi|Q8009611|qid=Q8009611|qid=Q8009611|lt=Kotoshironushi-no-Mikoto|1=Kotoshironushi-no-Mikoto}}
** {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Sumiyoshi Ōkami|qid=Q1114013|1=Sumiyoshi sanjin}}
** {{ill|lt=Haniyasuhime|Q9285919|qid=Q9285919|lt=Haniyama Ōkami|1=Haniyasu-hiko and Haniyasu-hime}}

=== History ===
It is a {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Shikinaisha|1=Shikinaisha|qid=Q134917286}} said to have been {{ill|lt=kanjō|Q1146687|qid=Q1146687|1=Cuy}}-enshrined by {{ill|lt=Sangi|Q1133663|qid=Q1133663|1=Sangi (Japan)}} {{ill|lt=Tachibana no Naramaro|Q7673717|qid=Q7673717|1=Tachibana no Naramaro}} in {{ill|lt=789|Q31558|qid=Q31558|1=789}} (Enryaku 8). There is a record that in {{ill|lt=851|Q29966|qid=Q29966|1=851}} (Ninju 1), it was granted Senior Sixth Rank. In the {{ill|lt=Jishō|Q1194671|qid=Q1194671|1=Jishō}} era (1177-1181), four deities were enshrined in the {{ill|lt=aidono|Q135009883|qid=Q135009883|1=Aidono}}. In {{ill|lt=1876|Q7766|qid=Q7766|1=1876}} (Meiji 9), it was ranked as a {{ill|lt=Sonsha|Q134917284|qid=Q134917284|1=Son-sha}}, and in Meiji 15 it was promoted to {{ill|lt=Gōsha|Q134917316|qid=Q134917316|1=Gō-sha}}.

=== Festivals ===
* Annual festival
:Held on April 10.

